OL,5, Billpayers, charities and businesses   
OL,6, are being urged to give their views on 
OL,7, daily standing charges on energy bills,
OL,8, as part of a review,                   
OL,10,FRegulator Ofgem said it wanted to open 
OL,11,Fthe debate over the charges, including 
OL,12,Fopinions on how to change the system.  
OL,14,FCurrently, energy customers pay a fixed
OL,15,Fdaily charge covering the costs of     
OL,16,Fconnecting to a supply.                
OL,18,FBut there has been anger about         
OL,19,Fincreasing fees and customers'         
OL,20,Finability to reduce what they pay.     
